item.title: Artilly
item.description: Artilly is a great YBBB from our Arti x Lilly pairing. Arti is one of our favorite ybbb breeders who we mixed in at the 3rd gen and Lilly is a female from our Jude x Kako group. We did not get too many examples from the small clutch that produced her, so it will be a lot of fun to prove her out! Artilly Artilly1 Artilly2 Filial F4-CG13 Sire Arti Dam Lilly 5 Generation Tree
